{"tid":553043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[空間跳躍!]【蘋民直擊】兩車切線撞 躁狂的哥傷人兼扑車","createTime":"2018-02-07T05:59:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-09T16:27:16.000Z","uid":65346,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5d7904c65edcd3c454c3bf5d6e506d1943c46a58","tid":553043,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T05:59:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180207/57802481\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180207%2F57802481&d=%2Bqx%2FnILicYbrFbax23IFzZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=8f1892be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180207%2F57802481&h=f6829d9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180207/57802481</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180207/large/1517978083_6277.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180207%2Flarge%2F1517978083_6277.jpg&h=6179263a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n旺角太子道西帝京酒店對開，上午11時40分，有的士與小巴相撞，事件中無人受傷，但的士司機非常激動，衝上小巴大吵大鬧，打司機、踢門、扯斷車窗扶手，再用硬物狂砸小巴車身。有途人勸說：「唔好咁衝動啦叔叔，大家搵食啫！」事後他涉嫌襲擊及刑事毀壞被捕。<br />\n<br />\n讀者曾先生目擊事件經過，他估計兩車是切線時碰撞。曾說：「個的士司機衝上小巴，發晒火。」從他拍攝的片段可見，穿著藍色外套紅色帽之的士司機，在小巴上踢門，狂扯車窗的扶手，將它扯斷後即由車窗跳落地，再由自己的士的車尾箱，取出千斤頂，狂砸小巴車門。<br />\n的士和小巴上各有乘客，有女途人勸說：「唔好咁衝動啦叔叔，大家搵食啫！」但他未有理會，繼續吵鬧。曾先生未有等候警員到場便離開，他認為事件中的司機無理性，認為發生交通意外「報警解決咪得囉！」<br />\n警方到場調查，小巴司機被毆受傷送院治理。其時，的士司機已冷靜下來，並顯得有悔意，欲走上救護車向小巴司機道歉，但被警員勸止，事後將他送院檢查。<br />\n記者事後在醫院向涉事陳姓的士司機了解事件，他坦承有襲擊對方司機。他說：「嬲囉，佢有心撞我㗎！塞緊車，邊有人咁樣撞埋嚟㗎，『嘭』一聲撞埋嚟！」他指自己讓前面另一小巴先行，但肇事小巴卻撞向他，慨嘆萬多元「墊底費」泡湯。"},{"pid":"d16c23a1917610ed593e71925ed57bde1eb571cf","tid":553043,"uid":65346,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T06:01:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nk-g6ax-ByI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dnk-g6ax-ByI&d=%2Bqx%2FnILicYbrFbax23IFzZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=5a7a8e6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nk-g6ax-ByI</a>"},{"pid":"a56e2b39b5664838dc0affd7c29e6617d84ecd5c","tid":553043,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T06:01:51.000Z","msg":"阿Ｕ　get !<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beb46ac03af6d61d486f549a48485422b0416606","tid":553043,"uid":161709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T06:07:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f387388b164b0bfc1f037ce1164fadfb6aaea5a","tid":553043,"uid":41974,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T06:08:54.000Z","msg":"打到飛起"},{"pid":"683b7d487201e6257c02f1e32f2bec88b992e133","tid":553043,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T08:57:16.000Z","msg":"又係的士狗"},{"pid":"d977500ae0f99d366133bd39291248af4a8337c2","tid":553043,"uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"683b7d487201e6257c02f1e32f2bec88b992e133","tid":553043,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T08:57:16.000Z","msg":"又係的士狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T08:59:03.000Z","msg":"席席BIRD 極　！"},{"pid":"5b74b274bf3356ee477ff2afd55da0e7170803a6","tid":553043,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T08:59:59.000Z","msg":"平時硬CUT人線果陣會唔會嬲自己?"},{"pid":"94655f64ddb9703005043dc2b6e0ae7f1c4b6418","tid":553043,"uid":65346,"like":1,"